===Format===
*'''Group Stage:''''' December 23th - 24th, 2024
** 64 teams, 2 matchdays.
*** 32 invited teams.
*** 32 qualified teams from Open Qualifiers.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 3 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams from each group}} (Total 32 teams) advance to the Semi Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams from each group}} are eliminated.

*'''Semi Finals:''''' December 25th - 26th, 2024
** 32 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** Each group will play 3 matches per day.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams from overall standings}} advance to the Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 16 teams}} are eliminated.

*'''Grand Finals:''''' December 27th - 29th, 2024
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
** Total of 18 matches (6 matches per day).

